graph LR
    subgraph 平台主机
        APP[应用组件]
        APP -->|结构化日志| LOG[标准输出 / 容器日志]
        APP -->|健康自检| HEALTH[健康检查通道]
        APP -->|指标暴露| METRIC[指标通道]
    end

    subgraph 外部对接
        LOG --> LOG_PLATFORM[客户日志平台<br/>ELK / Graylog / Loki]
        HEALTH --> MONITOR[运维监控]
        METRIC --> METRIC_PLATFORM[客户监控平台<br/>Prometheus + Grafana]
    end
